sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AIPanel as AIPanel<br/>(React)
    participant AIStore as aiStore<br/>(Zustand)
    participant Bridge as tauri-bridge
    participant AiCmd as commands/ai.rs
    participant ClaudeAPI as claude_api.rs
    participant Anthropic as api.anthropic.com

    User->>AIPanel: Types message + Enter
    AIPanel->>AIStore: setStreaming(true)
    AIPanel->>Bridge: aiChat(message, context)
    Bridge->>AiCmd: invoke("ai_chat", ...)
    AiCmd->>AiCmd: Generate request_id
    AiCmd-->>Bridge: { request_id, conversation_id }
    Note over AiCmd: Spawns async task

    AiCmd->>ClaudeAPI: send_message_streaming(key, model, prompt, messages, on_event)
    ClaudeAPI->>Anthropic: POST /v1/messages (stream: true)
    Anthropic-->>ClaudeAPI: HTTP 200 + SSE stream

    loop For each SSE chunk (bytes_stream)
        ClaudeAPI->>ClaudeAPI: Buffer bytes, parse lines
        alt data: {"type":"content_block_delta"}
            ClaudeAPI->>AiCmd: on_event(TextDelta(text))
            AiCmd->>AIPanel: emit("ai:stream-chunk", {request_id, text})
            AIPanel->>AIStore: appendStreamText(text)
            AIStore->>AIPanel: Re-render with streaming text
        end
        alt data: {"type":"message_delta"}
            ClaudeAPI->>ClaudeAPI: Capture stop_reason, output_tokens
        end
    end

    ClaudeAPI->>AiCmd: on_event(Completion(metadata))
    AiCmd->>AIPanel: emit("ai:stream-end", {request_id, model, tokens})
    AIPanel->>AIStore: setStreaming(false)
    AIPanel->>AIPanel: Finalize message in local state
